#compdef maelstrom-worker
# Documentation: source-direct extraction from upstream
# maelstrom-software/maelstrom —
#   crates/maelstrom-worker/src/config.rs lines 13-80
#     (Config struct: 8 flags, 3 with `hide` attribute)
# Reference accessed: 2026-05-30 via gh api.
#
# maelstrom-worker is the **Maelstrom worker daemon** —
# the per-node job executor that connects to a broker
# (R240's maelstrom-broker) and runs job specifications
# from clients (R238 cargo-maelstrom + R239 trio).  Workers
# are stateless: pull a job from the broker, execute it
# (typically inside a container), return results.  Scale
# horizontally by running more workers.
#
# Critical extraction note: maelstrom-worker uses **the same
# ClientConfig flag set as R238's cargo-maelstrom but
# WITHOUT the `flatten` flatten** — instead it duplicates the
# flag set verbatim in its own Config struct.  This is an
# upstream code-duplication choice (not using #[config
# (flatten)]) — likely because the worker has slightly
# different defaults (e.g. `broker` is mandatory for TCP
# rather than defaulting to standalone mode).  Documents
# that even within the same project, not every shared flag
# set goes through the #[config(flatten)] composition layer.
#
# Critical extraction note: `-b`/`--broker` flag at config.
# rs:18-22 has a **mandatory-for-TCP error message** — the
# default value `"no default, must be specified if cluster-
# communication-strategy is tcp (the default)"` is a STRING
# literal that gets printed if the user forgets to provide
# it.  Continues the corpus's documentation of
# context-dependent default values (R236 evcc's dual-purpose
# binary, R239 maelstrom-run's --escape-char tri-syntax).

_arguments -s -S \
  '(-h --help)'{-h,--help}'[show help and exit]' \
  '(-V --version)'{-V,--version}'[show version and exit]' \
  '(-b --broker)'{-b+,--broker=}'[broker socket address (REQUIRED if cluster-communication-strategy=tcp; default)]:sockaddr:' \
  '--slots=[number of job slots available (default: CPU count)]:n:' \
  '--cache-root=[directory for the cache (default: $XDG_CACHE_HOME/maelstrom-worker)]:path:_files -/' \
  '--cache-size=[target disk space for cache (SI/binary suffixes)]:bytes:' \
  '--inline-limit=[max bytes returned inline for stdout/stderr]:bytes:' \
  '(-L --log-level)'{-L+,--log-level=}'[min log level (default info)]:level:(error warn info debug trace)' \
  '--cluster-communication-strategy=[(HIDDEN) cluster strategy]:strategy:(tcp github)' \
  '--github-actions-token=[(HIDDEN) ACTIONS_RUNTIME_TOKEN]:token:' \
  '--github-actions-url=[(HIDDEN) ACTIONS_RESULTS_URL]:url:_urls'
